    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Green chilies from Hatch, N.M., are making their annual visit to Kitchen, 218 Eighth Avenue (21st Street), and this year the shop will roast these moderately hot peppers for you. All you have to do is peel and dice or stuff them -- a fresh soft cheese would be nice. Roasted or unroasted, they are $3.95 a pound and are available until Sept. 15.</p>
      </block>
